{"tid":549992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新年期間最熱門活動","createTime":"2018-02-04T09:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T00:48:54.000Z","uid":22938,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad92a903287aa7238814b9ae865106d9db7441e","tid":549992,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"活動名稱：新年攻防戰<br />\n時間：每年新年期間<br />\n地點：自己屋企<br />\n參加人數：不定<br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n親戚作為攻擊方，自己作防守方，<br />\n由攻擊方入屋開始，防守方要盡力保護自身財物，<br />\n直到攻擊方拜完年才算結束。<br />\n<br />\n攻擊方勝利方法：<br />\n成功拿走/破壞防守方的財物。<br />\n防守方勝利方法：<br />\n自身財物0損失並得到利是。<br />\n<br />\n注意：<br />\n1.攻擊方會以多種原因令被拿走/破壞財物的行為強行合理化。<br />\n2.攻擊方有機會在防守方不知情的情況下進行突擊拜年。<br />\n<br />\n參加方法：基本為強制性參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a63ccb815d99d64613ac0b80e7f390f1615ce8","tid":549992,"uid":20942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"7f9653761c115b8321a4f71fd61b8b37114c2a4e","tid":549992,"uid":32810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野？"},{"pid":"1c167f79179377fd5f089488e14664519c2d4a8a","tid":549992,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"如果有錯有缺漏，請指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cc9afb8f31a640364a783ac738a7b6fe43d839","tid":549992,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"18c219a84d9918b60a822778f68dc88acf7f17fa","tid":549992,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T00:48:54.000Z","msg":"？"}]}